{"tid":1663322,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(有圖慎入) 有手足派文宣 比藍屍用刀劏肚 腸都流埋出黎","createTime":"2019-10-19T10:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T11:31:45.000Z","uid":222970,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"176608183c5bc0b4b5924997b1dae772ce6da396","tid":1663322,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:48:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">入面圖 下次見到有左膠話唔好打藍屍 比佢睇張相<br />\n<br />\n各位係時候要將獅鳥再次升級</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/8ormPom.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8ormPom.jpg&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoKEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=9b8f706f\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/8ormPom.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n大埔發生斬人案，下午5時許，有街坊於大埔連儂隧道派傳單期間，一名黑衫男子將牆上的memo紙撕下，其間與街坊爭執，黑衫男突然取出利刀襲擊一名男街坊的頸部，傷者倒地後，狂徒再上前向其腹部刺一刀，腸臟外露，狂徒逞兇後登上的士離去。警方其後接報到場，將傷者送往沙田威爾斯醫院搶救。"},{"pid":"1195a2f71715209bb2462b6cd6ee418cd43621dd","tid":1663322,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:48:24.000Z","msg":"陳帆：港鐵如不再受破壞一、兩周內可回復正常服務<br />\n咩話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我要攬炒"},{"pid":"aa40f20a03273c16add60fefa6d99929ba62564b","tid":1663322,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:49:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62fb7fbdf59b5a4e031f5e26b8fff2ea0e413124","tid":1663322,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:49:56.000Z","msg":"簡直係謀殺<br />\n<br />\n【輸出革命】一齊下載強國文宣圖！<br />\n1020 尖東<span style=\"color: red;\">向強國人<strong>輸出革命</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1663011\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1663011</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j4oszVJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj4oszVJ.jpg&h=a9ec52d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http